data.allRelevantTextIncludingURLs: JD McPherson is performing at the Wonder Ballroom in Portland, Oregon on November 18. More info can be found at https://monqui.com/event/jd-mcpherson/wonder-ballroom/portland-oregon/. Tickets can be purchased at https://www.etix.com/ticket/p/95841402/jd-mcpherson-portland-wonder-ballroom?partner_id=100. Katie Gavin will also perform at the Wonder Ballroom on November 20. More information is available at https://monqui.com/event/katie-gavin-2/wonder-ballroom/portland-oregon/.
